flowRoot.flowPara: MediaGoblin is built by a vibrant and powerful community of people like you.
There are lots of ways to keep up with what's happening in the MediaGoblin world:
- Add the blog's RSS feed to your favorite reader
- Follow us on identi.ca, Twitter or Diaspora
- Talk to us on IRC in the #mediagoblin channel
Anyone can join us to improve the project!
The perfect tool to host and share your media
